{"tid":1188611,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同公司女同事食飯.....","createTime":"2019-06-06T11:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T12:57:36.000Z","uid":108548,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c5a5c7272b0a041c6ed64b28219bfea32e5e07","tid":1188611,"uid":108548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我一直都只會鐘意搵啲志同道合嘅人食飯 <br />\n咁小弟新入職就搵咗一個合眼緣嘅女同事同我一齊食飯<br />\n諗住試探下佢係咪我想搵嘅人<br />\n<br />\n我地去咗一間要㩒服務鐘叫人黎落單嘅飯店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：女同事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：做乜㩒極都無反應嘅？（舉手叫侍應）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你個嘢壞咗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： （原本飲緊茶，一嘢噴落我塊面到） 唔好意思（忍笑）<br />\n<br />\n咁個侍應走咗之後  佢又飲咗啖嘢 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 唉 屌 濕撚哂（擦件衫）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： （再噴多次） .....<br />\n<br />\n直到今日放工我地都無講過嘢 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 諗住今日唔洗塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a08d4c7be022b1b4872a1d3bd12cd1ea56f5e24","tid":1188611,"uid":211362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ba499584ea2832a640f94831bb83b15f55db86","tid":1188611,"uid":7015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"你試吓背潮文佢應該會腿張開俾你上"},{"pid":"51b3d15e05f67ab16dd679338b1a3826fef14b61","tid":1188611,"uid":186844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"-1/10 錯格式 扣1分"},{"pid":"c0e38389d